An '''appendix''' was an organ that became inflamed in beings, particularly [[Human/Legends|Humans]]. One Human major from [[Bakura/Legends|Bakura]] that [[Kornell Divini]] attended to had an appendix that had traveled to a different spot in his chest and grew to four times its normal size.

